---
import SiteLayout from "@layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
const title = `Home | Mille's Corner`
---

<style>
  ul#spreadsheet-links a {
    @apply link-primary;
  }
</style>

<SiteLayout title={title}>
  <main class="prose mx-auto max-w-3xl py-8 px-4 sm:px-8">
    <section class="card bg-base-200 p-8 md:p-12">
      <h1>Info</h1>
      <p>
        Hey, Mille here. I made a spreadsheet then I made another then another. Now there's an entire network of them.
      </p>
      <p>
        My goal is to help players make decisions on gear investment that suits their needs and budget, and help you
        understand how much damage you're truly dealing compared to someone else. Every spreadsheet below offers plenty
        of annotations to help you better understand the numbers shown and hopefully make them easier to use.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-2">
        If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to me on Twitter (<a href="https://twitter.com/mille_pso2"
          class="link link-hover link-secondary">@mille_pso2</a>). I'm also technically always <a
          class="link link-accent" href="/sandbird">recruiting for an alliance as well</a> if that interests you.
      </p>
      <h2 class="mb-0">Spreadsheet Links:</h2>
      <ul id="spreadsheet-links">
        <li>
          <h3>Gear Comparisons</h3>
          <a href="/weapons">Weapons</a> | <a href="/armors">Armor</a> | <a href="/augments">Augments</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>Calculators</h3>
          <a href="/damagecalculator">Damage Calculator</a> | <a href="/enhancement">Enhancement EXP Calculator</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3>Other</h3>
          <a href="/dropcharts">Drop Charts and Enemy Locations</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <div class="divider my-16"></div>

    <section class="prose card max-w-full bg-base-200 p-8 md:p-12" id="about">
      <h1 class="">Yo~!</h1>
      <h2 class="mt-0">
        <a href="https://twitter.com/jojobii_" class="link link-hover link-secondary">@jojobii</a>
        here...
      </h2>
      <p>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/mille_pso2" class="link link-hover link-secondary">@mille_pso2</a>
        said it'd be cool to have a more presentable hub for their resources
        for
        <em>The Hit Action MMORPG
          <a href="https://ngs.pso2.com/" class="link link-hover link-accent">Phantasy Star Online 2: New Genesis</a>
        </em>, so we're working on this together :3
      </p>
      <p>Typos or suggestions? Reach out to me on Twitter (<a href="https://twitter.com/jojobii_"
          class="link link-hover link-secondary">@jojobii</a>) or file an Issue on the <a
          class="link link-hover link-secondary" href="https://github.com/arks-moe/site-mille">GitHub Repo</a>!</p>
    </section>
  </main>
  <script>
    const $buttonCopyLink = document.querySelector('button#copy-link');
    $buttonCopyLink.addEventListener('click', () => {
      navigator.clipboard.writeText('https://mille.arks-sanctum.com/weapons');
    });
  </script>
</SiteLayout>
